title: Alex Jones Show - July 3 08 - Ron Paul, David Icke, Rima Laibow

Alex Jones Show
July 3, 2008
Ron Paul, David Icke, Rima Laibow & Bert Stubblebine

Alex also welcomes Dr. Ron Paul. Special guest today is David Icke, who recently announced he will run in Britain&#039;s parliamentary by-election.
